OL,3,CTeen died after being swept out to sea
OL,4,Con beach
OL,6,FA teenager drowned after he was swept
OL,7,Fout to sea while jumping waves with
OL,8,Ffriends on a beach, an inquest has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FDaniel Halliday, 14, was with two
OL,12,Fothers at Crosby Beach in Merseyside,
OL,13,Fwhen he was swept out to sea on 30
OL,14,FJune 2024, an inquest at Bootle Town
OL,15,FHall heard.
OL,17,FThe body of the teenager, from
OL,18,FTuebrook, Liverpool, was later
OL,19,Fdiscovered by an RNLI crew off the
OL,20,Fcoast at New Brighton, Wirral, on 8
OL,21,FJuly.
