OL,6,FSenior Coroner Julie Goulding ruled
OL,7,Fhis death, from drowning, was an
OL,8,Faccident.
OL,10,FShe said: "Tragically, the
OL,11,Fcatastrophic accident unfolded when
OL,12,Fthree young people were out having fun
OL,13,Ftogether and enjoying themselves."
OL,15,FOne of the youngsters with Daniel on
OL,16,Fthe day said they were jumping waves,
OL,17,Ftaking photos and having a "really
OL,18,Fgood time" at the beach.
