OL,6,FIn a statement read to the court, the
OL,7,Fboy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,8,Freasons, said the waves seemed to get
OL,9,Fbigger and their other friend was
OL,10,Fstruggling so he got out of the water
OL,11,Fwith her and shouted to Daniel to get
OL,12,Fon his back.
OL,14,FHe said he threw a life-ring to Daniel
OL,15,Fbut the rope was not long enough to
OL,16,Freach him.
OL,18,FHe said: "I was screaming and shouting
OL,19,Fbecause I was getting nowhere."
