OL,6,FLifeboats, the police helicopter, the
OL,7,Fcoastguard and fire and ambulance
OL,8,Fcrews were involved in the search for
OL,9,Fthe teenager, which was called off at
OL,10,F1am the following morning but resumed
OL,11,Fat first light.
OL,13,FMichael Buratti, area commander for HM
OL,14,FCoastguard, said Crosby was a
OL,15,F"relatively dangerous beach" because
OL,16,Fareas could be cut off by tides, there
OL,17,Fwas sinking mud and it was close to a
OL,18,Fbusy shipping channel in and out of
OL,19,Fthe River Mersey which could create
OL,20,Fwaves.
