OL,6,FMichelle Williams, from Sefton
OL,7,FMetropolitan Borough Council, said the
OL,8,Flife ring used to try to rescue Daniel
OL,9,Fwas not put in place by the council,
OL,10,Fbut was likely to have been put there
OL,11,Fby a "well meaning member of the
OL,12,Fpublic".
OL,14,FThe inquest heard it would not have
OL,15,Fbeen effective for rescuing someone in
OL,16,Fthat area.
OL,18,FMs Williams said there were 35 signs
OL,19,Falong the 3.4km stretch of beach which
OL,20,Fadvised that it was not a bathing
OL,21,Fbeach and warned of the dangers.
