OL,6,FDaniel's family told the inquest signs
OL,7,Fhad been faded when they visited the
OL,8,Farea.
OL,10,FHis mother Paula Heaton said: "They
OL,11,Fwere all dull and all washed out,
OL,12,Fthey're not going to attract a child's
OL,13,Feye."
OL,15,FThe coroner said it was a "positive
OL,16,Fstep" that there were plans by the
OL,17,Fcouncil to put more, larger signs in
OL,18,Fplace.
